# Tutorial: Intermediate - Step 1: Claude Code Settings
# Shows: Managing Claude Code configuration

Output intermediate-01-claude.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 900
Set Height 550
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 15
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

# Title
Type "# Intermediate: Claude Code Integration"
Enter
Sleep 1s

# View current settings
Type "ait claude settings"
Enter
Sleep 3.5s

# Show specific section
Type "ait claude settings --section approvals"
Enter
Sleep 3s

# List auto-approval presets
Type "ait claude approvals list"
Enter
Sleep 3s
